s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:11:"description";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:1452:"<p>If you live in the Northern Ohio area, make plans to stop by <a href="http://www.waterstreettavern.com/">Water Street Tavern</a> in Kent, OH Saturday, May 25th from 7PM-10PM to help us celebrate the 10th anniversary of WordPress. There will be a cash bar, good food and from what I&#8217;ve read, there might actually be some WordPress swag. This event is an excellent opportunity to wear the <a href="http://hellomerch.com/collections/wordpress/products/wordpress-10th-anniversary-t-shirt">special 10th anniversary t-shirt</a>. </p>\n<p>If you don&#8217;t live in Northern Ohio, check out the following <a href="http://www.meetup.com/WordPress/?see_all=1">list of WordPress parties</a> taking place this weekend to see if one is happening near you. </p>\n<div class="yarpp-related-rss">\n<p>Related posts:<ol>\n<li><a href="http://www.wptavern.com/10-year-anniversary-project-entry" rel="bookmark" title="10 Year Anniversary Project Entry">10 Year Anniversary Project Entry</a></li>\n<li><a href="http://www.wptavern.com/ohio-wordpress-meetup-april-23rd" rel="bookmark" title="Ohio WordPress Meetup April 23rd">Ohio WordPress Meetup April 23rd</a></li>\n<li><a href="http://www.wptavern.com/first-wordpress-weekly-listening-party" rel="bookmark" title="First WordPress Weekly Listening Party">First WordPress Weekly Listening Party</a></li>\n</ol></p>\n</div>\n<img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/WordpressTavern/~4/7Aj6DhnDJ6I" height="1" width="1" />";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:7:"pubDate";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:31:"Mon, 20 May 2013 16:15:25 +0000";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:32:"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/";a:1:{s:7:"creator";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:6:"Jeffro";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit"